txt.en: Far under Mount Gundabad lies the Den of Pughlak, the realm of the deepest of the deep toads.
You have defeated the Spectral Mûmak and overcome the questioning of reality.
You have defeated the candles and overcome a skewed perception.
You have defeated the Thunder-storm and overcome a fractured memory.
You have defeated the Cog-lurker and overcome the stalled mind.
You have defeated the Mind-crawlers and overcome clouded thoughts.
You have defeated the Raging Corraler and overcome racing notions.
Far under Mount Gundabad lies the Den of Pughlak, the realm of the deepest of the deep toads.
